ignoring case
	if ((characters 1 through 4 of ClipURL as string) is not "http") then
		return "Malformed URL."
	else
		set curlCMD to ¬
			"curl --stderr /dev/null \"http://api.bit.ly/v3/shorten?login=rogwilco&apiKey=R_87c8a48578cc138615ea32bf472ebd3e&format=txt&uri=" & ClipURL & "\""

		set tinyURL to (do shell script curlCMD)

		return tinyURL
	end if
end ignoring
